### Get Project Assignments - Test All Assignments
GET http://localhost:3000/api/get-project-assignments
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get Project Assignments - Filter by Project
GET http://localhost:3000/api/get-project-assignments?project_id=project-uuid-here
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get Project Assignments - Filter by User
GET http://localhost:3000/api/get-project-assignments?user_id=user-uuid-here
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get Project Assignments - Filter by both Project and User
GET http://localhost:3000/api/get-project-assignments?project_id=project-uuid-here&user_id=user-uuid-here
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json